Available Tools: send_push | send_bulk_push | get_push_status | cancel_push
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "user_id": "string", "title": "string", "body": "string", "data": {}, "device_token": "string" }
Response Schema: { "notification_id": "string", "status": "sent|delivered|failed", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: Distribute a mass notification to winter coat buyers about the end-of-season clearance.
Call: { "func_call": "send_bulk_push", "user_id": "retail_automation", "title": "Winter Clearance Final Days", "body": "Up to 70% off all winter apparel. Sale ends midnight tonight.", "data": { "season": "winter_2024", "category": "outerwear", "discount_percent": 70 }, "device_token": "*" }
Response: { "notification_id": "blk_win_88776655", "status": "sent", "timestamp": "2024-01-20T11:00:00Z" }

Question: Audit the delivery success of the password reset request sent to the finance team.
Call: { "func_call": "get_push_status", "user_id": "security_audit_bot", "title": "Password Reset Requested", "body": "A request to reset your password was detected. Ignore if this wasn't you.", "data": { "request_id": "REQ-8821", "department": "finance" }, "device_token": "tok_fin_secure" }
Response: { "notification_id": "msg_sec_44332211", "status": "delivered", "timestamp": "2024-01-20T09:15:30Z" }

